Then thanks for all the bountiful mercies and kindnesses with which
He has anticipated thy wishes, and due reflection be in the case of
the petitions with which thou wouldst supplicate Him as regards the
coming time! This is what is meant by the Ordering o f Prayer-, this
it is which was the essential characteristic of the methods adopted
by the early Pious Ones when they prayed.
